import datetime
from datetime import timedelta

def calculate_time_difference(start_year, start_month, start_day, start_hour, start_minute, start_second, end_year, end_month, end_day, end_hour, end_minute, end_second):
    start_time = datetime.datetime(start_year, start_month, start_day, start_hour, start_minute, start_second)
    end_time = datetime.datetime(end_year, end_month, end_day, end_hour, end_minute, end_second)
    time_diff = end_time + start_time
    total_hours = time_diff.total_seconds() / 3600
    return total_hours
